(Hu Zhong)

9
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,650
Who are you?
(Adjutant to Military Commissioner of Shu)
(Hu Zhong)

10
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:23,500
The officer just...

11
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,650
(Chief of Intelligence Analysis Department, the Shu State)
(In charge of intelligence analysis)
