12
00:02:27,650 --> 00:02:29,400
I'm Gao Tangbing, Chief of the Intelligence Analysis Department.
(Chief of Intelligence Analysis Department, the Shu State)
(In charge of intelligence analysis)
(Gao Tangbing)

13
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:32,000
Oh, Chief Gao.

14
00:02:33,730 --> 00:02:34,570
Be seated, please.

15
00:02:40,170 --> 00:02:41,579
In the Jieting's false intelligence case,

16
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:43,220
you're kind of

17
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:44,860
a witness.

18
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,700
I serve in the military.

19
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:49,180
But due to my low position,

20
00:02:49,650 --> 00:02:51,610
I didn't actually see what happened.

21
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,700
In your opinion,

22
00:02:53,950 --> 00:02:55,220
was Baidi tricked by Wei spies

23
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:57,930
so that he gave the false intelligence

24
00:02:57,950 --> 00:02:59,840
or did Baidi betray us

25
00:03:00,020 --> 00:03:02,130
and collude with Wei spies?

26
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,240
It's hard to judge, I'm afraid.

27
00:03:10,110 --> 00:03:12,940
Our department is mainly in charge of intelligence analysis.

28
00:03:13,170 --> 00:03:14,980
The Operations Department

29
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,410
distinguishes the sources of intelligence.

30
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:20,020
Is Baidi

31
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:22,410
always contacted by Clerk Feng personally?

32
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:26,540
The lurk of Baidi

33
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:29,530
has been a top secret of Siwencao Intelligence.

34
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:32,010
I only heard about him later.

35
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:33,420
Have you heard

36
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,020
of Wei's Qingping Plan?

37
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,329
Yes.

38
00:03:39,890 --> 00:03:42,079
It's been in operation for over a year,

39
00:03:42,420 --> 00:03:45,500
aiming to steal the crossbow technique from our army.

40
00:03:45,829 --> 00:03:46,940
Not exactly.

41
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:50,260
According to Chief Yin of the Operations Department,

42
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:52,300
Qingping Plan is a huge plan,

43
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:54,050
including many sub-plans

44
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,570
such as stealing our top military secrets,

45
00:03:56,930 --> 00:03:59,160
instigating our military and political leaders,

46
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:01,580
and inciting civil strife in the Han Dynasty.

47
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,530
Can Baidi's betrayal

48
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:04,690
be part of

49
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,350
the Qingping Plan?

50
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:09,090
At war,

51
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:11,380
Wei spies have been trying desperately

52
00:04:11,410 --> 00:04:12,960
to infiltrate Siwencao Intelligence.

53
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:14,390
It's not strange, is it?

54
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:17,540
Write it down.

55
00:04:17,850 --> 00:04:18,490
Aye.

56
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:22,180
Over the years,

57
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,490
Siwencao Intelligence has been like a dilapidated house

58
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:25,800
with leaks in all directions.

59
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:27,510
No secrets can be hidden.

60
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:31,630
Chief Gao, you're a senior member.

61
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,790
Do you have any advice for it?

62
00:04:36,730 --> 00:04:38,210
The rectification in Siwencao Intelligence

63
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:40,409
carried out by General Li

64
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,960
proves to be quite necessary.

65
00:04:49,110 --> 00:04:52,040
(Tianshui, the Wei State)

66
00:05:02,790 --> 00:05:04,000
The inn has been searched.

67
00:05:04,810 --> 00:05:06,480
Nobody suspicious is found.

68
00:05:07,690 --> 00:05:09,050
The murderer must be still in the old town.

69
00:05:10,870 --> 00:05:12,260
On the wall of the backyard,

70
00:05:12,470 --> 00:05:14,230
we found traces of grappling hooks.

71
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,370
Our men are going after him.

72
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,230
Keep hunting him.

73
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:17,290
Aye.

74
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,150
Looks like

75
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,630
you're quite lucky today.

76
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,170
I keep winning.

77
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:37,580
Thank you.

78
00:05:46,470 --> 00:05:48,920
Recorder Chen, come back and have fun.

79
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,100
Coming.

80
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:52,420
Set the game.

81
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,460
Here.

82
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,580
Wrong. Here.

83
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:00,860
Recorder Chen, what happened out there?

84
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,910
Out there...

85
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:04,250
Someone died.

86
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,420
Someone died?

87
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:07,790
What bad luck!

88
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:46,500
(Chief Clerk of Siwencao Intelligence, the Shu State)
(Yao You)

89
00:06:49,150 --> 00:06:52,340
Clerk Feng, General Hu Zhong invited you to the meeting room.

90
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:14,020
I've heard a lot about you.

91
00:07:14,790 --> 00:07:16,510
Clerk Feng, it's my honor

92
00:07:16,530 --> 00:07:17,690
to talk with you.

93
00:07:17,730 --> 00:07:18,700
Don't flatter me.

94
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:19,920
Just get to the point.

95
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:24,500
Ordered by General Li Yan,

96
00:07:24,650 --> 00:07:25,890
I'm having a talk with you,

97
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,730
mainly to confirm the punishment

98
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:29,860
of the traitor, Baidi.

99
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:32,250
We sent two batches of spies

100
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:34,060
to investigate this case.

101
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:36,920
The first batch of spies was killed.

102
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:38,980
For the second time,

103
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,240
Deputy Chief Xun Xu

104
00:07:40,650 --> 00:07:42,610
was assigned to the Wei State for the investigation

105
00:07:42,710 --> 00:07:43,790
and he would handle the traitor if necessary.

106
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:46,340
You decided whom to send

107
00:07:46,850 --> 00:07:48,300
to Tianshui for the investigation, right?

108
00:07:48,650 --> 00:07:49,370
Yes.

109
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:53,470
What's the problem?

110
00:07:53,890 --> 00:07:55,060
Why did you send Xun Xu?

111
00:07:57,890 --> 00:08:00,220
The duty of the Internal Affairs Department is to find out traitors.

112
00:08:01,670 --> 00:08:03,320
Xun Xu is the Deputy Chief of the Internal Affairs Department.

113
00:08:04,170 --> 00:08:06,140
He hasn't done any fieldwork before.

114
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,280
He is quite inexperienced.

115
00:08:10,380 --> 00:08:12,230
But in this false intelligence case,

116
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:13,740
he turns out to be the most innocent.

117
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,590
The Military Intelligence Agency of Wei

118
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:18,620
doesn't have any chance

119
00:08:18,620 --> 00:08:19,620
to approach or subvert him.

120
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:23,380
But he's said to be Baidi’s brother-in-law.

121
00:08:24,490 --> 00:08:25,530
I've never heard about that.

122
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:29,030
Is it possible

123
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:31,260
that Xun Xu would let Baidi off?

124
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,030
We have precautions

125
00:08:35,470 --> 00:08:36,919
against this kind of situation.

126
00:08:37,309 --> 00:08:38,700
Before leaving,

127
00:08:39,059 --> 00:08:40,740
Xun Xu drank the farewell tea of Siwencao Intelligence.

128
00:08:41,370 --> 00:08:43,289
He won't get the antidote until he completes his mission?

129
00:08:43,650 --> 00:08:44,370
Right.

130
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,640
It's the old rule

131
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:48,390
for difficult fieldwork.

132
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,080
Any other questions?

133
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:57,880
Hurry.

134
00:08:58,110 --> 00:08:59,460
(Military Intelligence Agency of Wei)
(Tianshui, the Wei State)

135
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,020
Keep up.
(Military Intelligence Agency of Wei)
(Tianshui, the Wei State)

136
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:02,170
(Military Intelligence Agency of Wei)
(Tianshui, the Wei State)

137
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,980
I guess the killer realized that Gu Zheng was exposed.

138
00:09:04,050 --> 00:09:06,280
He then killed him to cut off the clues.

139
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,890
Put them to torture and interrogate them.

140
00:09:10,170 --> 00:09:10,850
Aye.

141
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:13,270
Chancellor Mi,

142
00:09:13,690 --> 00:09:15,080
we caught a Shu soldier alive.

143
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,850
Where's he?

144
00:09:16,460 --> 00:09:17,730
He's being interrogated in the prison.

145
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,780
He said nothing before passing out.

146
00:09:33,110 --> 00:09:34,830
All Shu soldiers on Xiaolong Mountain are dead,

147
00:09:35,090 --> 00:09:36,090
but him.

148
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:39,800
Get a physician for him.

149
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,870
Make him talk,

150
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:44,100
at whatever cost.

151
00:09:45,690 --> 00:09:47,130
Gu Zheng is

152
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,080
a dead end.

153
00:09:50,110 --> 00:09:51,100
What are we going to do next?

154
00:09:53,290 --> 00:09:55,100
Have two of our capable henchmen

155
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:57,880
keep a close eye on Chen Gong day and night.

156
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:01,190
Record everything he does.

157
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:03,380
If he knows what Governor is planning,

158
00:10:03,530 --> 00:10:04,570
there'll be another tempest.

159
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:37,030
Today, Chen Gong made a reckless move.

160
00:10:38,230 --> 00:10:39,990
He'll give himself away soon.

161
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,660
Keep a close eye on him and leave everything else alone.

162
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,830
All right. I'll do it personally.

163
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:57,110
Jili Carriage Shop was searched.

164
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,890
Servants and shop assistants

165
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:01,030
were all put in prison.

166
00:11:02,970 --> 00:11:04,090
He was used.

167
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,330
Used?

168
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:11,700
He said he not only contacted you,

169
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:14,910
but also a spy named Chidi in Tianshui.

170
00:11:19,310 --> 00:11:20,070
Impossible.

171
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:21,600
That's impossible.

172
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:25,560
Feng Ying made it clear

173
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:28,860
that Gu Zheng was my exclusive agent

174
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:30,940
for safety concerns

175
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:33,400
and he would never get involved in any other events.

176
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:34,380
No way.

177
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:35,860
Right.

178
00:11:37,090 --> 00:11:38,300
In Siwencao Intelligence,

179
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,870
I've never heard of Chidi, either.

180
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:44,670
How did they contact?

181
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,790
By shooting arrows.

182
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:47,290
They never met.

183
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,480
I'm afraid our deduction was right.

184
00:11:58,330 --> 00:12:00,590
Zhulong takes a senior occupation in Siwencao Intelligence.

185
00:12:01,290 --> 00:12:04,320
He made up the codename, Chidi.

186
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:07,620
Without knowing the truth,

187
00:12:07,650 --> 00:12:08,800
Gu Zheng became his agent.

188
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:12,940
Now, Gu Zheng is dead.

189
00:12:14,810 --> 00:12:16,530
We can't vindicate ourselves.

190
00:12:19,700 --> 00:12:21,610
Looks like I have to take the blame

191
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:24,100
for the Jieting's false intelligence case.

192
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:24,980
Yeah.

193
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,560
Jieting was lost and the Northern Expedition failed.

194
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:30,390
Such a big case

195
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:32,620
can't be let go unless you're executed.

196
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:35,260
I'm in a desperate plight.

197
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:42,990
(Li Yan’s Camp)
(Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

198
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:47,290
General,

199
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:50,380
this is the list of upper-middle administrators of Siwencao Intelligence.

200
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:53,280
They're all slyboots.

201
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:55,000
A group of slippery fellows.

202
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:57,170
Did you talk to all of them?

203
00:12:57,650 --> 00:12:58,690
Yes.

204
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:00,550
Feng Ying is kind of interesting.

205
00:13:01,090 --> 00:13:03,060
He's always been on Yang Yi's side.

206
00:13:04,170 --> 00:13:07,140
But he isn't completely loyal to Yang Yi.

207
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,780
After Baidi betrayed us,

208
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:12,620
Yang Yi asked Feng Ying to close the case quickly

209
00:13:12,830 --> 00:13:14,180
and leave no loopholes for us.

210
00:13:14,410 --> 00:13:16,200
Unexpectedly, he had something in reserve.

211
00:13:18,710 --> 00:13:19,790
Feng Ying...

212
00:13:20,690 --> 00:13:21,990
Don't do anything to him yet.

213
00:13:22,990 --> 00:13:25,310
Keep him working in Siwencao Intelligence.

214
00:13:25,780 --> 00:13:27,580
But arrange an assistant for him.

215
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:29,520
Have one of our men

216
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:31,190
work for him.

217
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:34,310
Not you.

218
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:38,190
You must stay with me.

219
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,110
General,

220
00:13:48,810 --> 00:13:50,780
I have someone to recommend.

221
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:51,820
Who?

222
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:54,700
He's Li Miao.

223
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:57,540
He isn't on the list.

224
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,660
Li Miao

225
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:00,470
used to be

226
00:14:00,570 --> 00:14:01,980
a counsellor at the Prime Minister's Mansion.

227
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:03,820
He was demoted to a plebeian

228
00:14:03,970 --> 00:14:06,180
and he hates Yang Yi's gut.

229
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:07,730
It was he who told me

230
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:09,400
about Wei spies

231
00:14:09,530 --> 00:14:11,690
inside Siwencao Intelligence.

232
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:12,540
Is he reliable?

233
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:13,580
Yes, I guess.

234
00:14:14,830 --> 00:14:16,190
Where's he?

235
00:14:17,230 --> 00:14:19,700
After being demoted by Zhuge Liang, he had nowhere to go

236
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:23,330
and he came to me for shelter. Now he's in Nanzheng County.

237
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:28,830
Take him to me first.

238
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,310
We've got a way out.

239
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:35,540
Come on.

240
00:14:36,090 --> 00:14:37,240
Don't try to console me anymore.

241
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:38,310
I'm serious.

242
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:40,470
There's a man

243
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,520
who knows the existence of Zhulong.

244
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,000
As long as he testifies...

245
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:47,080
Guo Gang.

246
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:48,070
Mm.

247
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:51,780
How would he testify?

248
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:53,350
Let's get him to Nanzheng County.

249
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,240
You're insane.

250
00:14:55,990 --> 00:14:58,220
Only he can prove the existence of Zhulong

251
00:14:58,730 --> 00:14:59,920
so that we can both get out of the problem.

252
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:01,920
This is ridiculous.

253
00:15:02,380 --> 00:15:03,780
From Tianshui to Nanzheng County,

254
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:05,030
how can we avoid so many Wei soldiers?

255
00:15:05,350 --> 00:15:06,860
With a good plan,

256
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,720
we may stand a chance.

257
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:11,860
Even if I fail to survive,

258
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,720
I must at least die vindicating myself.

259
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,580
You've got a plan?

260
00:15:16,910 --> 00:15:17,860
We have to

261
00:15:19,170 --> 00:15:20,210
take Guo Gang away secretly

262
00:15:20,230 --> 00:15:21,310
and stop Wei soldiers

263
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,340
from catching up with us within a day.

264
00:15:24,050 --> 00:15:25,900
We can't even do the second part.

265
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,650
Guo Gang is crazy

266
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,500
about newfangled craft.

267
00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:34,060
He once ordered me

268
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:37,230
to restore Lu Ban's Bamboo Kite.

269
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:39,030
Bamboo Kite?

270
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:40,230
As recorded in history,

271
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:43,600
Lu Ban made a kite of bamboo.

272
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:46,470
It kept flying in the sky for three days.

273
00:15:47,430 --> 00:15:48,520
But it's just a legend.

274
00:15:48,940 --> 00:15:51,780
In the 13th year of Jian'an Period (208 A.D.), the Wei Army reached Xinye.

275
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:55,490
Liu Cong had his envoy offer a declaration of surrender and welcome Cao Cao to Jingzhou.

276
