00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:51,240
with this kite?

553
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:54,030
Hundreds of meters with the help of wind.

554
00:29:54,330 --> 00:29:55,090
Hundreds of meters?

555
00:29:56,130 --> 00:29:56,940
Quite enough.

556
00:29:58,570 --> 00:29:59,380
Governor,

557
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:01,160
what else do you want to use it for?

558
00:30:03,990 --> 00:30:06,640
Do you think I'm only crazy about newfangled craft?

559
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:08,000
No, I don't.

560
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:11,290
This is about the fate of our state.

561
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,030
By the way,

562
00:30:13,290 --> 00:30:14,570
I've got a plan to carry out.

563
00:30:16,650 --> 00:30:17,580
You're needed for it.

564
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,560
Let's get back to my mansion.

565
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,040
Mm.

566
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,930
According to the intel,

567
00:30:37,530 --> 00:30:40,650
the latest types of crossbows made by Shu's Military Technology Department

568
00:30:40,820 --> 00:30:43,540
can shoot twenty arrows in succession.

569
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:45,070
Extremely lethal.

570
00:30:45,690 --> 00:30:46,690
They're available for cavalry and infantry.

571
00:30:47,510 --> 00:30:50,550
The old type of crossbow could only shoot five arrows in succession.

572
00:30:51,220 --> 00:30:53,700
Looks like the Shu Army has made great progress in weapons.

573
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:55,600
The latest types of crossbows

574
00:30:56,020 --> 00:30:57,940
are named Shudu and Yuanrong.

575
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,350
Soon,

576
00:30:59,410 --> 00:31:01,170
the Shu Army will be equipped with them.

577
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:03,480
It'll cause great pressure on our army.

578
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:07,040
It sounds quite different

579
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:07,970
from what we used to know.

580
00:31:08,380 --> 00:31:09,790
To protect the secret,

581
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:11,270
the Shu Army has set up

582
00:31:11,670 --> 00:31:13,510
countless fake workshops.

583
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:15,990
Thanks to Zhulong,

584
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:19,280
we've confirmed the head office.

585
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:22,740
It's in the west of Mount Dingjun.

586
00:31:23,580 --> 00:31:26,020
There's a canyon among the cliffs.

587
00:31:26,700 --> 00:31:30,140
Only one way leads to the head office.

588
00:31:33,980 --> 00:31:34,660
Um...

589
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:36,930
With three lines of defense,

590
00:31:37,390 --> 00:31:38,470
this place is strongly fortified.

591
00:31:39,050 --> 00:31:39,920
How can we get in?

592
00:31:40,450 --> 00:31:41,490
Before,

593
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,670
we couldn't sneak in.

594
00:31:45,570 --> 00:31:46,690
But things are different now.

595
00:31:48,410 --> 00:31:50,200
Chen Gong, why don't you tell Mi Chong

596
00:31:50,870 --> 00:31:51,660
how we can get in?

597
00:31:51,740 --> 00:31:52,820
Chancellor Mi.

598
00:31:57,520 --> 00:31:59,340
The head office. The cliff.

599
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:01,110
The cliff.

600
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,240
The head office.

601
00:32:04,250 --> 00:32:05,000
The cliff?

602
00:32:05,660 --> 00:32:06,380
You can get in?

603
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:10,500
You'll fly over?

604
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:13,840
No way, unless you were a bird.

605
00:32:18,380 --> 00:32:19,540
He could be a bird.

606
00:32:19,750 --> 00:32:20,510
He could?

607
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:24,900
Very well, then.

608
00:32:39,450 --> 00:32:41,770
With this, we can sneak into the head office

609
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,960
of Shu's Military Technology Department by surprise

610
00:32:44,260 --> 00:32:45,810
and collaborate with Zhulong

611
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:49,530
to get the drawings of their latest crossbows.

612
00:32:50,230 --> 00:32:50,980
Governor,

613
00:32:52,060 --> 00:32:55,130
shouldn't we test if it can really fly?

614
00:32:56,470 --> 00:32:57,150
Governor,

615
00:32:57,810 --> 00:33:00,250
I plan to try it in a day or two.

616
00:33:02,100 --> 00:33:03,710
In other cases,

617
00:33:03,730 --> 00:33:05,610
I would like to go with you.

618
00:33:05,660 --> 00:33:06,710
But I can't go this time.

619
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:08,180
This is a matter of great importance.

620
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:09,940
Neither you nor I can take this risk.

621
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:12,560
I'll have someone else test the Bamboo Kite.

622
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:15,060
-You're so thought...
-Governor,

623
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:18,060
who will you send for this mission?

624
00:33:19,250 --> 00:33:20,930
Someone from your agency.

625
00:33:22,330 --> 00:33:23,090
How about...

626
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:25,990
How about Liang Jian?

627
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:28,100
He can go with Recorder Chen.

628
00:33:32,300 --> 00:33:32,940
What's wrong?

629
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:33,720
Governor,

630
00:33:35,010 --> 00:33:37,540
I'm not good at fieldwork.

631
00:33:38,030 --> 00:33:38,680
I know.

632
00:33:38,710 --> 00:33:40,580
So, I asked Liang Jian to go with you.

633
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,270
Chen Gong,

634
00:33:45,620 --> 00:33:47,270
I mean to promote you.

635
00:33:47,700 --> 00:33:49,630
If you want a promotion,

636
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:52,910
you have to make practical achievements.

637
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:56,020
Thank you, Governor.

638
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:58,050
I'll try my best.

639
00:33:58,760 --> 00:34:00,690
All you need to care about is the Bamboo Kite.

640
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:02,470
As long as it can fly over the canyon,

641
00:34:02,490 --> 00:34:04,290
leave the rest to Liang Jian.

642
00:34:05,830 --> 00:34:07,200
If you have no more questions,

643
00:34:07,220 --> 00:34:08,370
go back and get prepared.

644
00:34:08,469 --> 00:34:09,340
Leave in three days...

645
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,120
Governor,

646
00:34:11,969 --> 00:34:13,239
I have

647
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,630
a small question.

648
00:34:14,730 --> 00:34:15,650
May I have a word with you?

649
00:34:17,020 --> 00:34:17,429
All right.

650
00:34:28,429 --> 00:34:30,270
Why are you so mistrustful of Chen Gong?

651
00:34:30,530 --> 00:34:33,080
Yesterday, when we were hunting for Shu spies,

652
00:34:34,060 --> 00:34:36,300
he appeared there and it was quite suspicious.

653
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,730
I know you don't trust him.

654
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:39,590
But only he can

655
00:34:39,940 --> 00:34:41,770
assemble and operate the Bamboo Kite.

656
00:34:41,810 --> 00:34:42,570
What do you suggest, then?

657
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:43,949
I do have a suggestion.

658
00:34:44,570 --> 00:34:45,199
I'm all ears.

659
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:47,010
Don't let Liang Jian go.

660
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:48,560
Let me go instead.

661
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:56,429
It sounds feasible.

662
00:34:57,680 --> 00:34:59,720
But you're a chancellor of Military Intelligence Agency

663
00:34:59,750 --> 00:35:01,390
and he's a recorder in Tianshui.

664
00:35:01,410 --> 00:35:03,720
If you disappear at the same time,

665
00:35:03,740 --> 00:35:05,880
Shu spies will notice that.

666
00:35:06,410 --> 00:35:07,620
Don't underestimate them.

667
00:35:11,030 --> 00:35:12,340
It's not a problem.

668
00:35:13,650 --> 00:35:17,000
Arrange a horse accident on the mountain route

669
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:19,030
and claim that Recorder Chen and I die in it.

670
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:20,270
What do you think?

671
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:22,760
Fine, then.

672
00:35:23,390 --> 00:35:24,020
I'll let you go with him.

673
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:25,710
Thank you, Governor.

674
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:29,390
You must pay attention to two points.

675
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:31,350
First, Qingping Plan is

676
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:33,290
carried out by Commander himself.

677
00:35:33,890 --> 00:35:36,820
Getting the drawings of Shu's crossbows is our big plan.

678
00:35:37,230 --> 00:35:38,820
Don't take it personally.

679
00:35:38,850 --> 00:35:40,000
And you mustn't fail the mission.

680
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,500
Second,

681
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:44,480
Chen Gong is a talent.

682
00:35:45,720 --> 00:35:48,310
Keep him safe and sound.

683
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:49,840
Got it.

684
00:35:50,410 --> 00:35:51,220
I'll protect him.

685
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:54,580
I mean it.

686
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:20,740
Guo Gang asked you to go to the Shu State?

687
00:36:23,250 --> 00:36:24,400
It's a great opportunity.

688
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:28,360
We planned to kidnap Guo Gang

689
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:30,260
but it was quite risky.

690
00:36:30,750 --> 00:36:33,020
And he might not speak for us.

691
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:35,900
In this mission,

692
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:37,900
can you see Zhulong?

693
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,120
I'm very likely to see him.

694
00:36:40,550 --> 00:36:41,350
Awesome.

695
00:36:42,890 --> 00:36:43,720
Guo Gang worried

696
00:36:44,910 --> 00:36:47,540
that when Mi Chong and I disappeared at the same time,

697
00:36:48,180 --> 00:36:50,070
Siwencao Intelligence would notice that.

698
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:51,950
Mi Chong came up with an idea.

699
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:54,430
He would arrange a horse accident

700
00:36:54,870 --> 00:36:56,820
where he and I would die

701
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:57,810
for the state.

702
00:36:58,930 --> 00:36:59,920
When I “die”,

703
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:02,760
you can get out of trouble, too.

704
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,140
At last, I can go back to report on my mission.

705
00:37:10,330 --> 00:37:10,730
Mm.

706
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:24,180
But our organization believes you betrayed us.

707
00:37:24,690 --> 00:37:27,320
Your identity as Baidi may be exposed at any time.

708
00:37:27,750 --> 00:37:30,560
If Zhulong knows you’re Baidi...

709
00:37:30,590 --> 00:37:32,830
I'll kill Mi Chong halfway

710
00:37:34,490 --> 00:37:35,970
and take his place.

711
00:37:37,290 --> 00:37:38,730
From then on,

712
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,850
Chen Gong will no longer exist.

713
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:47,340
But you also have to deceive the Military Intelligence Agency.

714
00:37:47,370 --> 00:37:48,300
It's in no way easy.

715
00:37:49,130 --> 00:37:50,600
To cover the whole story,

716
00:37:50,970 --> 00:37:52,010
you need a perfect plan.

717
00:37:52,980 --> 00:37:53,700
What?

718
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:56,940
You don't trust me?

719
00:38:01,610 --> 00:38:03,090
Things are finally turning around.

720
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:07,800
Feng Ying

721
00:38:08,590 --> 00:38:10,700
gave you a poisonous dagger.

722
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:11,840
Leave it to me.

723
00:38:17,980 --> 00:38:19,170
Be very careful.

724
00:38:19,610 --> 00:38:20,020
Mm.

725
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:23,660
This time,

726
00:38:24,740 --> 00:38:26,100
our contact person

727
00:38:26,130 --> 00:38:27,620
will be Huang Yu,

728
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,510
the senior of Wuxian Sect.

729
00:38:38,770 --> 00:38:40,020
Oh, Wuxian Sect.

730
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:43,790
Then you can see Di Yue.

731
00:38:46,270 --> 00:38:47,420
That's great.

732
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:50,110
When you work with your wife, you'll make a difference.

733
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:55,650
Tomorrow morning,

734
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:56,780
you shall leave Tianshui, too.

735
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:58,150
Don't dwell in a dangerous place.

736
00:38:58,900 --> 00:38:59,740
Have a pleasant trip.

737
00:39:00,050 --> 00:39:00,770
Have a pleasant trip, too.

738
00:39:19,690 --> 00:39:20,540
What a pity!

739
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:23,060
We nearly got him cornered.

740
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:26,580
What else can we do?

741
00:39:28,910 --> 00:39:30,390
Governor made his decision

742
00:39:31,690 --> 00:39:32,770
and he won’t change his mind.

743
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:35,000
When Chen Gong reaches the Shu State,

744
00:39:35,890 --> 00:39:36,820
he will do something.

745
00:39:37,430 --> 00:39:38,900
It's not a bad thing.

746
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:42,740
When he's out there,

747
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:46,490
he'll have some space to maneuver.

748
00:39:47,290 --> 00:39:48,640
But once he's in the Shu State,

749
00:39:49,820 --> 00:39:50,860
it'll be hard to control him.

750
00:39:51,330 --> 00:39:52,860
I'll play it by ear.

751
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:55,620
If something goes wrong,

752
00:39:56,180 --> 00:39:58,190
I'll kill him there.

753
00:39:58,820 --> 00:39:59,780
It's too dangerous.

754
00:39:59,810 --> 00:40:01,410
You mustn't let him see Zhulong.

755
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:05,830
Stop nagging.

756
00:40:06,970 --> 00:40:07,880
How's the soldier

757
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:09,580
you captured alive on Xiaolong Mountain?

758
00:40:11,580 --> 00:40:12,960
I asked the physician to use some tough medicine

759
00:40:13,230 --> 00:40:14,470
and the soldier barely survived.

760
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:15,900
However,

761
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:17,280
he's still in a coma.

762
00:40:17,620 --> 00:40:18,700
Those Shu soldiers

763
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:20,500
saw Baidi before.

764
00:40:22,090 --> 00:40:24,560
You must wake him up and make him confess.

765
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:25,700
I see.

766
00:40:26,040 --> 00:40:28,670
I'll count on you for business here.

767
00:40:29,660 --> 00:40:30,300
Mm.

768
00:40:51,410 --> 00:40:54,020
(Chen Gong’s wife, the Shu State)
(Di Yue)

769
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:57,870
Be serious.

770
00:41:01,460 --> 00:41:02,270
Eat the meat from the same plate.

771
00:41:05,900 --> 00:41:06,670
Hurry.

772
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:19,330
Drink the wine.

773
00:41:29,610 --> 00:41:30,420
Eat the meat again.

774
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:36,670
Do it again.

775
00:41:42,550 --> 00:41:43,310
Be serious.

776
00:41:52,110 --> 00:41:52,870
Drink the wine again.

777
00:42:03,250 --> 00:42:04,130
Eat the meat one more time.

778
00:42:06,380 --> 00:42:07,550
Be serious, will you?

779
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:22,880
Drink the wine in the gourds.

780
00:42:45,090 --> 00:42:45,920
The ceremony is over.

781
00:42:51,140 --> 00:42:51,900
From this day on,

782
00:42:52,580 --> 00:42:54,170
you're husband and wife.

783
00:43:12,970 --> 00:43:16,060
(The 24 Strategies of War, The Wind Blows from Longxi)
(Intelligence Agency in Longxi)

784
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:19,290
(The Fourth Strategy)
(Covering the Dagger with a Smile)

785
00:43:21,030 --> 00:43:21,610
Feng Ying,

786
00:43:22,140 --> 00:43:22,610
you see?

787
00:43:23,050 --> 00:43:23,900
Exactly as I predicted.

788
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:25,420
Once General Li Yan

789
00:43:25,860 --> 00:43:27,020
took over Siwencao Intelligence,

790
00:43:27,370 --> 00:43:29,410
he closed the case concerning Baidi

791
00:43:29,670 --> 00:43:30,910
and planted his henchmen in every department

792
00:43:31,570 --> 00:43:33,370
through a reshuffle.

793
00:43:33,510 --> 00:43:35,060
Now even Hu Zhong

794
00:43:35,090 --> 00:43:36,740
is on an equal footing to us.

795
00:43:36,740 --> 00:43:38,020
There's more to it than what is said.

796
00:43:38,020 --> 00:43:39,060
And their sneers.

797
00:43:39,190 --> 00:43:39,990
How irritating!

798
00:43:41,200 --> 00:43:42,510
The Wei plans

799
00:43:42,540 --> 00:43:44,540
a field mission for Chen Gong and Mi Chong.

800
00:43:44,540 --> 00:43:46,700
Guo Gang makes up a horse incident

801
00:43:46,700 --> 00:43:47,900
and their death,

802
00:43:47,900 --> 00:43:50,110
so the two can stay undercover

803
00:43:50,130 --> 00:43:51,700
in Wuxian Sect

804
00:43:51,700 --> 00:43:53,580
where they will find a way to steal

805
00:43:53,580 --> 00:43:54,820
drawings of our latest crossbows.

806
00:43:54,820 --> 00:43:56,900
Speaking of Guo Gang and Mi Chong,

807
00:43:56,900 --> 00:43:58,420
Guo Gang is the governor

808
00:43:58,420 --> 00:43:59,790
of Tianshui, the Wei State

809
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:00,970
and also the nephew

810
00:44:00,990 --> 00:44:02,310
of Guo Huai,

811
00:44:02,340 --> 00:44:03,900
the founder of Military Intelligence Agency

812
00:44:03,900 --> 00:44:05,100
of the Wei State.

813
00:44:05,300 --> 00:44:07,160
Both Military Intelligence Agency

814
00:44:07,180 --> 00:44:08,150
and Siwencao

815
00:44:08,180 --> 00:44:09,580
are spy agencies

816
00:44:09,580 --> 00:44:10,980
of the Wei

817
00:44:10,980 --> 00:44:12,210
and the Shu States.

818
00:44:12,320 --> 00:44:14,200
The Military Intelligence Agency

819
00:44:14,220 --> 00:44:15,290
is the counterpart

820
00:44:15,310 --> 00:44:16,390
of Siwencao.

821
00:44:16,420 --> 00:44:17,650
So Chen Gong gaining

822
00:44:17,670 --> 00:44:18,590
Guo Gang's trust

823
00:44:18,620 --> 00:44:20,260
is of great significance

824
00:44:20,260 --> 00:44:22,260
for Siwencao to gather internal intelligence

825
00:44:22,260 --> 00:44:23,980
of the Wei State.

826
00:44:24,180 --> 00:44:26,690
Mi Chong is the leader of Military Intelligence Agency.

827
00:44:27,020 --> 00:44:28,680
As an ace spy,

828
00:44:28,700 --> 00:44:30,340
he's trusted by his boss

829
00:44:30,340 --> 00:44:32,130
and determined to capture

830
00:44:32,130 --> 00:44:33,740
the Shu spy

831
00:44:33,740 --> 00:44:35,010
in the Wei State.

832
00:44:35,210 --> 00:44:37,500
He sets his eyes on Chen Gong.

833
00:44:37,500 --> 00:44:38,060
So,

834
00:44:38,060 --> 00:44:39,900
